Here's the PlantUML component diagram for the `davidlandry93_glo4001` system focusing on connectivity:

```plantuml
@startuml davidlandry93_glo4001

package "3D Rendering Core" {
    [Three.js] as threejs
    [Potree] as potree
    [WebGLRenderer] as webgl
    [Shader System] as shaders
}

package "Robotic Control" {
    [Robot Controller] as robot
    [Sensor Manager] as sensors
    [ROS Bridge] as ros
}

package "Data Processing" {
    [Point Cloud Processor] as pc_processor
    [CZML Processor] as czml
    [ICP Algorithm] as icp
}

package "User Interface" {
    [GUI Controller] as gui
    [Visualization] as viz
}

threejs --> potree : uses\npoint cloud\nrendering
threejs --> webgl : delegates\nrendering
threejs --> shaders : manages\nmaterials

robot --> ros : sends/receives\ncommands
sensors --> ros : publishes/subscribes\nto topics
ros --> pc_processor : forwards\nsensor data

pc_processor --> potree : feeds\npoint clouds
pc_processor --> icp : uses for\nregistration
czml --> threejs : provides\ntime-dynamic\nobjects

gui --> threejs : controls\nrendering\nparameters
gui --> robot : sends\ncontrol\ncommands
viz --> threejs : displays\n3D scene
viz --> sensors : shows\nsensor data

@enduml
```